<D>__{hello.}
<A>__{artoo beeps in response. luke unplugs artoo and begins to scrape several connectors on the robot's head with a chrome pick. threepio climbs out of the oil tub and begins wiping oil from his bronze body.}
<C>__{luke}
<D>__{you got a lot of carbon scoring here. it looks like you boys have seen a lot of action.}
