<C>__{threepio}
<D>__{what is what?!? he asked you a question...}
<P>__{(pointing to leia)}
<D>__{what is that?}
<A>__{artoo whistles his surprise as he pretends to just notice the hologram. he looks around and sheepishly beeps an answer for threepio to translate. leia continues to repeat the sentence fragment over and over.}
